data.description: Nestled on a beautiful expansive lot in St. Charles is this amazing 3-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home that offers lovely finishes throughout and a spectacular boat dock with scenic views of the St. Charles Fox River! Step inside and discover a spacious family room adorned with a bay window. Adjoining it is a delightful dining room that fills with natural light. The kitchen is a true highlight, featuring an open concept design and a range of stainless-steel appliances, a nook area, and an extensive array of cabinetry, providing ample storage space. Enjoy a bar, an eating area with a stunning brick fireplace, and convenient access to your meticulously manicured backyard completed with a brick paver patio. Surrounded by lush greenery, this outdoor haven offers ample yard space to bask in the beauty of the warm months! Additionally, this home features a versatile area that can be transformed to suit your unique needs and preferences. The 2nd level features the marvelous Primary Bedroom with a stunning arched entry way to the Primary Bathroom that includes double vanities, and his and hers walk-in closets. There are also 2 generously sized bedrooms that share a wonderful full bathroom! The partially finished lower level features a full bathroom, and excess storage space! This home also boasts a 3-car garage!!! Local amenities, including top-rated schools, picturesque parks, delicious restaurants, and lovely shops are easily accessible. A very well taken care of home.
